63
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:32,272
[Haran] <i>Dia tahu wajah saya</i>

64
00:04:39,654 --> 00:04:41,239
dan nama saya.

65
00:04:42,198 --> 00:04:44,075
Sukacita berkenalan dengan awak.

66
00:04:45,285 --> 00:04:46,411
Ah…

67
00:04:46,494 --> 00:04:47,495
Senang bertemu dengan awak.

68
00:04:48,329 --> 00:04:49,497
Saya melihat awak dari dekat tadi,
melihat lukisan Sisley.

69
00:04:50,164 --> 00:04:53,459
Tidak…

70
00:04:55,086 --> 00:04:56,254
Ini tidak betul. Tidak.

71
00:04:56,838 --> 00:04:58,506
Tidak...

72
00:04:59,215 --> 00:05:00,216
<i>Hei, baunya seperti hujan.</i>

73
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:01,801
[Chan] <i>Itulah baunya</i>
<i>bahan organik meresap.</i>

74
00:05:01,884 --> 00:05:04,137
Petrichor.

75
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:05,471
[Haran] <i>Ada lelaki lain</i>
<i>yang bercakap seperti dia.</i>

76
00:05:05,555 --> 00:05:08,266
Dia tidak suka terung.

77
00:05:09,017 --> 00:05:10,601
